{"tid":1822942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Duckduckgo將成為歐盟Android設備的預測搜尋引擎選項","createTime":"2020-01-13T09:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T09:47:17.000Z","uid":156109,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f655e123467ee80a2e4c81d968f4c8c42f66e672","tid":1822942,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:27:34.000Z","msg":"DuckDuckGo將成為歐盟Android設備的替代搜索引擎選項。歐盟監管機構正強迫Google向Android用戶展示選擇選擇他們自己的替代搜索引擎。為非法，它向搜索巨人開出了50億美元的創紀錄罰單。 <br />\n<br />\n現在，Google必須提醒用戶在設置歐盟Android設備時選擇替代搜索引擎。在提供的搜索引擎選項中，隱私搜索引擎DuckDuckGo排在最前列，<a href=\"http://其他還有Info.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89Info.com&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=5fe72155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">其他還有Info.com</a>，Yandex，Qwant，GMX，PrivacyWall，Givero和Seznam，微軟的Bing只提供給英國用戶選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中文source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.cnbeta.com/view/931997.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.cnbeta.com%2Fview%2F931997.htm&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=7e18e024\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.cnbeta.com/view/931997.htm</a><br />\n<br />\neng source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.searchenginejournal.com/duckduckgo-is-now-a-default-search-engine-option-on-android-in-the-eu/343073/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.searchenginejournal.com%2Fduckduckgo-is-now-a-default-search-engine-option-on-android-in-the-eu%2F343073%2Famp%2F&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=f76c38b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.searchenginejournal.com/duckduckgo-is-now-a-default-search-engine-option-on-android-in-the-eu/343073/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"04787b271a4378276165996c7cb08edfaa1e8970","tid":1822942,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"好心唔好用google翻譯 啲中文一舊舊"},{"pid":"5b1a28d22916a09bf359257d5bbd172f84c7b4da","tid":1822942,"uid":249263,"like